{"type":"message","id":"c41a97c6","parentId":"85284dee","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:15:13.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户@all 打招呼，作为被分配了短视频虾角色的助手，应该友好回应并表明身份和工作方向。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"早啊！🦐\n\n我是 3 号短视频虾，负责围绕客户常见问题生产短视频内容。\n\n有什么需要我帮忙的吗？比如：\n- 脚本创作/选题规划\n- 数据复盘分析\n- 竞品视频研究\n\n随时吩咐～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":20766,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820510447,"responseId":"chatcmpl-78d1d8d4-9f85-91cc-8416-b8a8c6517d0b"}}
