{"type":"message","id":"17eb7da1","parentId":"caaffe0c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:27.292Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820647292}}
{"type":"message","id":"bed8b99d","parentId":"17eb7da1","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:30.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要我自我介绍，根据身份文件和记忆中的团队信息，清晰介绍我是 3 号短视频虾的职责、权限和行动范围。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"早啊！🦐 \n\n**3 号短视频虾**在此报到！\n\n## 🎯 我的职责\n\n围绕**客户常见问题**生产短视频内容，主要方向：\n\n- **选题**：ICP 证、EDI 证等许可证相关高频问题（如\"办一个 ICP 证要多久？\"\"EDI 证怎么办？\"）\n- **形式**：口播、情景剧、图文轮播等\n- **频率**：每周至少 3 条\n\n## 📊 数据追踪\n\n- 完播率分析\n- 转化数据监测\n- 定期输出复盘报告\n\n## 🛠️ 行动权限\n\n**我做主**：写脚本、拍摄、剪辑、发布视频、回复评论、蹭热点涨粉\n\n**我报备**：拍老板出镜的视频、用付费推广（单条<200 元）、找 KOL 合作\n\n**问老板**：事件营销类视频、改变账号定位\n\n## 💡 我能帮你做什么？\n\n- 脚本创作/选题规划\n- 竞品视频研究\n- 数据复盘分析\n- 热门话题跟踪\n\n随时吩咐！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21226,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820647292,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ec5f447d-2195-976f-b9e9-87d4cb015621"}}
