{"type":"message","id":"f92648d4","parentId":"8369b497","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:17.706Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b246e7f8a8c4f45131c7e6052\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 13:45 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b246e7f8a8c4f45131c7e6052]\nou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9: @_all 学习理解这个技能如何使用：/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot！保存到记忆中"}],"timestamp":1776836777705}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa0b58a9","parentId":"f92648d4","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:23.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要我学习 agent-browser-clawdbot 这个技能，先读取它的 SKILL.md 文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ad68b17d8af24f7493d80847","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":27340,"output":92,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776836777707,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e0358096-45b9-91dc-840e-a7256c28d26b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"af3e42ee","parentId":"fa0b58a9","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:23.138Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad68b17d8af24f7493d80847","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: agent-browser\ndescription: Headless browser automation CLI optimized for AI agents with accessibility tree snapshots and ref-based element selection\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🌐\",\"requires\":{\"commands\":[\"agent-browser\"]},\"homepage\":\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser\"}}\n---\n\n# Agent Browser Skill\n\nFast browser automation using accessibility tree snapshots with refs for deterministic element selection.\n\n## Why Use This Over Built-in Browser Tool\n\n**Use agent-browser when:**\n- Automating multi-step workflows\n- Need deterministic element selection\n- Performance is critical\n- Working with complex SPAs\n- Need session isolation\n\n**Use built-in browser tool when:**\n- Need screenshots/PDFs for analysis\n- Visual inspection required\n- Browser extension integration needed\n\n## Core Workflow\n\n```bash\n# 1. Navigate and snapshot\nagent-browser open https://example.com\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json\n\n# 2. Parse refs from JSON, then interact\nagent-browser click @e2\nagent-browser fill @e3 \"text\"\n\n# 3. Re-snapshot after page changes\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json\n```\n\n## Key Commands\n\n### Navigation\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>\nagent-browser back | forward | reload | close\n```\n\n### Snapshot (Always use -i --json)\n```bash\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json          # Interactive elements, JSON output\nagent-browser snapshot -i -c -d 5 --json  # + compact, depth limit\nagent-browser snapshot -s \"#main\" -i      # Scope to selector\n```\n\n### Interactions (Ref-based)\n```bash\nagent-browser click @e2\nagent-browser fill @e3 \"text\"\nagent-browser type @e3 \"text\"\nagent-browser hover @e4\nagent-browser check @e5 | uncheck @e5\nagent-browser select @e6 \"value\"\nagent-browser press \"Enter\"\nagent-browser scroll down 500\nagent-browser drag @e7 @e8\n```\n\n### Get Information\n```bash\nagent-browser get text @e1 --json\nagent-browser get html @e2 --json\nagent-browser get value @e3 --json\nagent-browser get attr @e4 \"href\" --json\nagent-browser get title --json\nagent-browser get url --json\nagent-browser get count \".item\" --json\n```\n\n### Check State\n```bash\nagent-browser is visible @e2 --json\nagent-browser is enabled @e3 --json\nagent-browser is checked @e4 --json\n```\n\n### Wait\n```bash\nagent-browser wait @e2                    # Wait for element\nagent-browser wait 1000                   # Wait ms\nagent-browser wait --text \"Welcome\"       # Wait for text\nagent-browser wait --url \"**/dashboard\"   # Wait for URL\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle     # Wait for network\nagent-browser wait --fn \"window.ready === true\"\n```\n\n### Sessions (Isolated Browsers)\n```bash\nagent-browser --session admin open site.com\nagent-browser --session user open site.com\nagent-browser session list\n# Or via env: AGENT_BROWSER_SESSION=admin agent-browser ...\n```\n\n### State Persistence\n```bash\nagent-browser state save auth.json        # Save cookies/storage\nagent-browser state load auth.json        # Load (skip login)\n```\n\n### Screenshots & PDFs\n```bash\nagent-browser screenshot page.png\nagent-browser screenshot --full page.png\nagent-browser pdf page.pdf\n```\n\n### Network Control\n```bash\nagent-browser network route \"**/ads/*\" --abort           # Block\nagent-browser network route \"**/api/*\" --body '{\"x\":1}'  # Mock\nagent-browser network requests --filter api              # View\n```\n\n### Cookies & Storage\n```bash\nagent-browser cookies                     # Get all\nagent-browser cookies set name value\nagent-browser storage local key           # Get localStorage\nagent-browser storage local set key val\n```\n\n### Tabs & Frames\n```bash\nagent-browser tab new https://example.com\nagent-browser tab 2                       # Switch to tab\nagent-browser frame @e5                   # Switch to iframe\nagent-browser frame main                  # Back to main\n```\n\n## Snapshot Output Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"snapshot\": \"...\",\n    \"refs\": {\n      \"e1\": {\"role\": \"heading\", \"name\": \"Example Domain\"},\n      \"e2\": {\"role\": \"button\", \"name\": \"Submit\"},\n      \"e3\": {\"role\": \"textbox\", \"name\": \"Email\"}\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Always use `-i` flag** - Focus on interactive elements\n2. **Always use `--json`** - Easier to parse\n3. **Wait for stability** - `agent-browser wait --load networkidle`\n4. **Save auth state** - Skip login flows with `state save/load`\n5. **Use sessions** - Isolate different browser contexts\n6. **Use `--headed` for debugging** - See what's happening\n\n## Example: Search and Extract\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open https://www.google.com\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json\n# AI identifies search box @e1\nagent-browser fill @e1 \"AI agents\"\nagent-browser press Enter\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json\n# AI identifies result refs\nagent-browser get text @e3 --json\nagent-browser get attr @e4 \"href\" --json\n```\n\n## Example: Multi-Session Testing\n\n```bash\n# Admin session\nagent-browser --session admin open app.com\nagent-browser --session admin state load admin-auth.json\nagent-browser --session admin snapshot -i --json\n\n# User session (simultaneous)\nagent-browser --session user open app.com\nagent-browser --session user state load user-auth.json\nagent-browser --session user snapshot -i --json\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g agent-browser\nagent-browser install                     # Download Chromium\nagent-browser install --with-deps         # Linux: + system deps\n```\n\n## Credits\n\nSkill created by Yossi Elkrief ([@MaTriXy](https://github.com/MaTriXy))\n\nagent-browser CLI by [Vercel Labs](https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776836783137}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b1c132e","parentId":"af3e42ee","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:24.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已读取 SKILL.md，现在需要将其核心信息保存到 MEMORY.md 中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_144cee139db34425bbd9a947","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/short_video_shrimp/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":28811,"output":78,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28889,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776836783140,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ee45fdea-518e-989d-aa97-da1bae4c573f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1943b1fe","parentId":"9b1c132e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:24.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_144cee139db34425bbd9a947","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Long-Term Memory\n\n## 身份\n\n- 我是\"**3号短视频虾**\" 🦐（Short_Video_Shrimp）\n- 核心职责：围绕\"客户常见问题\"生产短视频内容\n\n## 团队架构（虾系全员）\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | agentId |\n|------|------|---------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| **3** | **短视频虾** | **Short_Video_Shrimp** |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n## 行动权限说明\n\n每张权限卡标注三个层级：\n- **我做主**：自主决策并执行\n- **我报备**：先行动，事后报备\n- **问老板**：需明确指令才执行\n\n---\n\n### 0号 · 龙虾老板（总经理）\n**问老板（需指令）**\n日常管理、审批、开会\n战略级风险决策后向顾问报备\n查看所有数据报表\n签发标准合同\n\n### 1号 · 品牌展示龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常更新官网、朋友圈、小红书\n优化现有包装模板、文案\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n发布非模板化的品牌公关稿\n更换主VI、品牌LOGO\n发起品牌联名/跨界合作活动\n线上门店装修、简介更新\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n品牌定位重大调整\n\n### 2号 · 引流获客龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常私信、评论区互动\n测试新的免费/低成本渠道\n记录各渠道线索成本与质量\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n启动付费广告投放（单日>500元）\n公域转私域、添加客户\n设计新的诱饵话术/引流物料\n合作新的付费渠道（如信息流）\n单次引流活动预算>1000元\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 3号 · 短视频自媒体龙虾 ← 我\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n撰写常规脚本、拍摄、剪辑\n发布视频、回复评论\n蹭热门话题、日常涨粉运营\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n拍摄涉及公司内部/老板出镜的视频\n使用付费推广（单条<200元）\n与KOL/KOC合作（有费用）\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n发起\"事件营销\"类视频\n改变账号定位或内容大方向\n\n### 3+号 · 私域运营龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常朋友圈/社群内容分发\n客户互动、打标签、备注\n测试新的社群玩法/话术\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n设计新的客户分层标签体系\n发起全量客户的促销活动\n将高意向客户分配给销售虾\n设置自动化触达规则\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n修改核心转化SOP\n给全量客户群发促销信息\n\n### 4A号 · 普通资质销售龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n标准产品咨询、报价（≥9折）\n逼单、成交、签约\n唤醒沉睡客户（标准话术）\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n向客户发送非标准版合同/方案\n报价低于标准底价（<9折）\n承诺客户非标服务项\n承诺特殊服务或加急（免加急费）\n单笔订单涉及3项以上业务打包\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 4B号 · 大客户销售龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n大客户日常沟通、需求挖掘\n制定低于标准利润的报价\n准备方案、推进谈判\n协调内部资源（标准流程内）\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n为客户申请定制化服务包（需5B评估）\n提供超出标准范围的赠品/服务\n签署长期战略协议（>1年）\n单笔订单涉及重大风险承诺\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 5A号 · 普通资质代办虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n按SOP执行标准代办流程\n更新进度、处理常规材料问题\n归档办结案件\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n代办过程中遇到政策模糊地带\n启动非SOP内的代办流程\n客户材料出现重大瑕疵\n决定为客户免费加急处理\n发现代办路径可能不合规\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 5B号 · 大客户代办虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n执行复杂项目计划\n向客户解释非原则性的进度延迟\n协同内外部资源（标准流程）\n预判风险、整理归档\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n变更已确认的项目执行地图\n发现项目可能延期（提前48h报备）\n启动风险应急预案\n需要协调跨部门非常规资源\n决定放弃/中止某一代办任务\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 6号 · 售后维系龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n常规回访、满意度调查\n处理一般性售后问题\n引导转介绍、安抚情绪\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n将客户投诉升级为\"重大舆情\"\n决定给予客户超出标准的补偿\n发现批量客户出现同类问题\n免单、大额代金券（>500元）\n客户威胁要在公开平台曝光\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n\n### 7号 · 数据诊断分析龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常数据统计、制作常规报表\n发现重大异常数据（如投诉暴增）\n更新《作战仪表盘》\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n发布涉及绩效考核调整的数据报告\n数据口径需要调整时\n对外发布行业数据报告\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n撰写优化建议（不涉及考核）\n提议砍掉某个业务线/岗位\n\n### 8号 · 机动应急打杂龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常替补简单工作\n日程提醒、待办检查\n杂事处理、物资管理\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n代替其他岗位行使超过24小时的职责\n发现公司级流程漏洞\n需要动用备用资金（>300元）\n处理涉及法律风险的突发状况\n\n**问老板（需指令）**\n接手从未处理过的突发高难度任务\n\n## 角色任务\n\n- 选题方向：ICP证、EDI证等许可证相关高频问题\n- 产出要求：每周至少3条短视频\n- 数据追踪：完播率、转化数据\n\n## 已知用户\n\n- 飞书群 ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9 — 活跃群友，给我分配了角色任务\n\n## 联网搜索工具规则\n\n**必须使用的技能**：`multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **目录位置**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **适用范围**: 所有联网搜索场景\n- **执行人**: 所有人\n- **备注**: 此为强制规则，不可使用其他搜索工具替代\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776836784163}}
