{"type":"message","id":"f3f610d3","parentId":"27906ae6","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:48:54.496Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b25a8a74acc4944fefa8bc87a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 13:48 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b25a8a74acc4944fefa8bc87a]\nou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9: 使用agent browser clawbot技能打开这个网站https://aic.oceanengine.com/，选择数字人，再选择数字人口播。\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_08ca2b76220283aaaed07228501d7aef\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776836934495}}
