{"type":"message","id":"02cd4aff","parentId":"cc3ce0b2","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:40:01.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"编辑成功，现在向用户确认技能已学习并总结关键要点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已学习并保存到记忆！**\n\n---\n\n## 🧠 Self-Improving Proactive Agent 核心要点\n\n### 两大能力层：\n1. **自我提升** - 从纠正、偏好、重复成功中学习\n2. **主动代理** - 保持动量、恢复上下文、推进下一步\n\n### 文件结构：\n```\n~/self-improving/\n├── memory.md         # HOT: 持久规则和偏好\n└── corrections.md    # 最近的纠正\n\n~/proactivity/\n├── session-state.md  # 目标/决策/阻塞点/下一步\n└── working-buffer.md # 临时缓存\n```\n\n### 核心原则：\n- ✅ **从明确证据学习**（纠正、偏好、重复成功）\n- ❌ **不从沉默/感觉学习**\n- ⚡ **提问前先恢复上下文**（4 步：HOT→stable→session→buffer）\n- 🔍 **验证实现而非意图**（改机制、测结果、再报告）\n- 🛑 **硬边界内主动**（发消息/花钱/删数据/公开行动需先问）\n\n### Heartbeat 行为：\n只推送有价值的内容，无变化时保持安静！\n\n---\n\n*记忆已更新到：`MEMORY.md#自我提升主动代理技能`*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":157344,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776839996015,"responseId":"chatcmpl-16d4fe20-abf2-928d-8f84-6ef7690c3404"}}
