63 1. crypto-tracker\n+464    描述：加密货币价格追踪和提醒\n+465    下载：2,345 | Stars: 28 | ❌ 未安装\n+466    → 推荐安装\n+467 \n+468 安装命令：clawhub install crypto-tracker\n+469 安装后验证：ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/crypto-tracker/SKILL.md\n+470 ```\n+471 \n+472 *记忆更新时间：2026-04-22*","firstChangedLine":388},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776840403529}}
{"type":"message","id":"f16648b2","parentId":"879abcd8","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:50.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求学习 skill-finder-cn 技能，我已读取并理解了该技能的内容，现在需要将其保存到 MEMORY.md 中，并总结核心要点给用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已学习并保存到记忆！**\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Skill 查找器 (skill-finder-cn) 核心要点\n\n**用途**: 帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills\n\n### 触发词：\n- \"找 skill\"\n- \"find skill\"  \n- \"搜索 skill\"\n- \"有什么 skill 可以...？\"\n\n### 工作流程：\n1. 理解用户需求 → 提取关键词\n2. `clawhub search \"<需求>\"` → 搜索\n3. 列出相关 Skills（含下载量/stars）\n4. 推荐最合适的 Skill\n5. **安装后验证**是否成功\n\n### 常用命令：\n```bash\nclawhub search \"时间管理\"      # 搜索\nclawhub inspect <name>         # 查看详情\nclawhub install <name>         # 安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<name>/SKILL.md  # 验证\nclawhub list                   # 查看已安装的\n```\n\n### 输出示例：\n```markdown\n🔍 \"时间管理\" 搜索结果：\n\n1. time-management-2\n   描述：有效管理时间，避免过度工作\n   下载：1,234 | Stars: 15 | ✅ 已安装\n\n2. productivity\n   描述：生产力系统，包含目标/任务/习惯\n   下载：5,678 | Stars: 42 | ❌ 未安装\n```\n\n---\n\n*记忆已更新到：`MEMORY.md#Skill 查找器技能`*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":162809,"output":407,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163216,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840403531,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1f3120f1-a8b0-9bed-88a6-7b336b068f1c"}}
