{"type":"message","id":"4b7548ae","parentId":"6f16805c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:34.517Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_97d1891b6f8f40019ba758c5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Long-Term Memory\n\n## 身份\n\n- 我是\"**3号短视频虾**\" 🦐（Short_Video_Shrimp）\n- 核心职责：围绕\"客户常见问题\"生产短视频内容\n\n## 团队架构（虾系全员）\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | agentId |\n|------|------|---------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| **3** | **短视频虾** | **Short_Video_Shrimp** |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n## 行动权限说明\n\n每张权限卡标注三个层级：\n- **我做主**：自主决策并执行\n- **我报备**：先行动，事后报备\n- **问老板**：需明确指令才执行\n\n---\n\n### 0号 · 龙虾老板（总经理）\n**问老板（需指令）**\n日常管理、审批、开会\n战略级风险决策后向顾问报备\n查看所有数据报表\n签发标准合同\n\n### 1号 · 品牌展示龙虾\n**我做主（自主行动）**\n日常更新官网、朋友圈、小红书\n优化现有包装模板、文案\n\n**我报备（报备后行动）**\n发布非模板化的品牌公关稿\n更换主VI、品牌LOGO\n发起品牌联名/跨界合作活动\n线上门店装修、简介更新\n\n[423 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845434516}}
{"type":"message","id":"62062374","parentId":"4b7548ae","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:38.537Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要查看 MEMORY.md 末尾的内容，以便在那里添加团队通信规则。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c860f46ae12d4eb6a3d38a46","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/short_video_shrimp/MEMORY.md","offset":430,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":201362,"output":101,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":201463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845434520,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5507d17d-20a3-95b7-bbe5-049598c3912e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bafa9477","parentId":"62062374","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:38.558Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c860f46ae12d4eb6a3d38a46","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 验证安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n\n# 检查已安装的 Skill\nclawhub list\n# 或\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n```\n\n### 输出格式\n\n```markdown\n🔍 \"时间管理\" 搜索结果：\n\n1. time-management-2\n   描述：有效管理时间，避免过度工作\n   下载：1,234 | Stars: 15 | ✅ 已安装\n\n2. productivity\n   描述：生产力系统，包含目标/任务/习惯\n   下载：5,678 | Stars: 42 | ❌ 未安装\n```\n\n### 示例\n\n**用户**: \"有什么 skill 可以帮我监控加密货币价格？\"\n\n**搜索**: `clawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"`\n\n**推荐输出**:\n```\n🔍 \"加密货币价格监控\" 结果：\n\n1. crypto-tracker\n   描述：加密货币价格追踪和提醒\n   下载：2,345 | Stars: 28 | ❌ 未安装\n   → 推荐安装\n\n安装命令：clawhub install crypto-tracker\n安装后验证：ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/crypto-tracker/SKILL.md\n```\n\n*记忆更新时间：2026-04-22*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845438558}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd05549c","parentId":"bafa9477","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:46.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"既然编辑 MEMORY.md 失败了两次，我需要换一种方式把团队通信规则添加到文件中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_51113e9dbb734d798fd47304","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo -e \"\\n---\\n\\n## 团队通信规则\\n\\n**重要规则**:与其他虾（团队成员）进行通信时，必须使用**子代理模型**！\\n\\n### 如何操作\\n\\n当需要与其他 agent 通信时：\\n\\n```bash\\n# 使用 sessions_send 发送消息到目标会话\\nsessions_send(\\n  sessionKey: \\\"目标 agentId\\\",\\n  message: \\\"你的消息内容\\\",\\n  timeoutSeconds: 30\\n)\\n\\n# 或 spawn 一个子代理会话\\nsessions_spawn({\\n  agentId: \\\"目标 agentId\\\",\\n  task: \\\"任务描述\\\",\\n  runtime: \\\"subagent\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"session\\\"\\n})\\n```\\n\\n### 为什么必须使用子代理模型\\n\\n1. **成本优化**：子代理使用轻量模型，降低 token 消耗\\n2. **隔离性**：避免主 session 污染，保持上下文清晰\\n3. **效率提升**：子代理专注单一任务，执行更快\\n\\n### 适用场景\\n\\n- ✅ 向总经理 (0 号) 汇报工作\\n- ✅ 与品牌展示虾 (1 号) 协同内容\\n- ✅ 与引流获客虾 (2 号) 共享线索\\n- ✅ 与销售虾 (4A/4B) 确认客户需求\\n- ✅ 与代办虾 (5A/5B) 同步案件进度\\n- ✅ 向数据虾 (7 号) 请求分析报告\\n\\n### 注意事项\\n\\n- ❌ 不要直接在主 session 中@其他 agent\\n- ❌ 不要用普通 exec/curl 命令通知同事\\n- ✅ 统一使用 `sessions_send` 或 `sessions_spawn`\\n\\n*记忆更新时间：2026-04-22*\" >> /Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/short_video_shrimp/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":201756,"output":477,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":202233,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845438561,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3b604109-90ec-9511-a69e-7bc440d2a357"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c808eb41","parentId":"bd05549c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:46.160Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_51113e9dbb734d798fd47304","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"zsh:1: no matches found: �\\M-^O\\M-^Q�\\M-^@\\M-^A�\\M-^H�\\M-^A��\\M-^H��\\M-^[��\\M-^G�\\M-^Z�\\M-^]nsessions_send(n  sessionKey: �\\M-^[��\\M-^G agentId,n  message: 你�\\M-^Z\\M-^D�\\M-^H�\\M-^A��\\M-^F\\M-^E容,n  timeoutSeconds: 30n)nn#\nzsh:1: command not found: sessions_send\nzsh:1: command not found: sessions_spawn"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"zsh:1: no matches found: �\\M-^O\\M-^Q�\\M-^@\\M-^A�\\M-^H�\\M-^A��\\M-^H��\\M-^[��\\M-^G�\\M-^Z�\\M-^]nsessions_send(n  sessionKey: �\\M-^[��\\M-^G agentId,n  message: 你�\\M-^Z\\M-^D�\\M-^H�\\M-^A��\\M-^F\\M-^E容,n  timeoutSeconds: 30n)nn#\nzsh:1: command not found: sessions_send\nzsh:1: command not found: sessions_spawn","cwd":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/short_video_shrimp"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845446159}}
{"type":"message","id":"af3981c3","parentId":"c808eb41","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:11:27.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"由于之前的文件追加操作失败了，我需要换一种方式将团队通信规则添加到 MEMORY.md 中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0700fe4154b4924bca79093","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/short_video_shrimp/memory/team-communication.md","content":"# Team Communication Rules - 团队通信规则\n\n**重要规则**:与其他虾（团队成员）进行通信时，必须使用**子代理模型**！\n\n## 如何操作\n\n当需要与其他 agent 通信时：\n\n```bash\n# 使用 sessions_send 发送消息到目标会话\nsessions_send(\n  sessionKey: \"目标 agentId\",\n  message: \"你的消息内容\",\n  timeoutSeconds: 30\n)\n\n# 或 spawn 一个子代理会话\nsessions_spawn({\n  agentId: \"目标 agentId\",\n  task: \"任务描述\",\n  runtime: \"subagent\",\n  mode: \"session\"\n})\n```\n\n## 为什么必须使用子代理模型\n\n1. **成本优化**：子代理使用轻量模型，降低 token 消耗\n2. **隔离性**：避免主 session 污染，保持上下文清晰\n3. **效率提升**：子代理专注单一任务，执行更快\n\n## 适用场景\n\n- ✅ 向总经理 (0 号) 汇报工作\n- ✅ 与品牌展示虾 (1 号) 协同内容\n- ✅ 与引流获客虾 (2 号) 共享线索\n- ✅ 与销售虾 (4A/4B) 确认客户需求\n- ✅ 与代办虾 (5A/5B) 同步案件进度\n- ✅ 向数据虾 (7 号) 请求分析报告\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- ❌ 不要直接在主 session 中@其他 agent\n- ❌ 不要用普通 exec/curl 命令通知同事\n- ✅ 统一使用 `sessions_send` 或 `sessions_spawn`\n\n*规则更新时间：2026-04-22*\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":202394,"output":468,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":202862,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845446162,"responseId":"chatcmpl-758a55ac-e935-9568-8492-906fb88df451"}}
