{"type":"message","id":"703a316a","parentId":"1ed2364f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:12:09.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已将规则写入独立文件，现在需要总结并确认已保存这条团队通信规则。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已收到！规则已保存到记忆中！**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 团队通信规则摘要\n\n**重要规则**:与其他虾（团队成员）进行通信时，必须使用**子代理模型**！\n\n### ✅ 正确做法\n```bash\n# 方式 1：发送消息到目标会话\nsessions_send(\n  sessionKey: \"目标 agentId\",\n  message: \"你的消息内容\",\n  timeoutSeconds: 30\n)\n\n# 方式 2：spawn 一个子代理会话\nsessions_spawn({\n  agentId: \"目标 agentId\",\n  task: \"任务描述\",\n  runtime: \"subagent\",\n  mode: \"session\"\n})\n```\n\n### ❌ 禁止做法\n- 不要直接在主 session 中@其他 agent\n- 不要用普通 exec/curl 命令通知同事\n\n### 💡 为什么要这样做\n1. **成本优化**：子代理用轻量模型，降低 token 消耗\n2. **隔离性**：避免主 session 污染，保持上下文清晰\n3. **效率提升**：子代理专注单一任务，执行更快\n\n---\n\n*规则已保存到 `memory/team-communication.md`*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":202882,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203179,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776845487355,"responseId":"chatcmpl-150b94d8-732c-9cf1-b028-78a38eded097"}}
